	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64117915"><p>Have you ever tried to contribute code to a large open source project? Good luck with that! They have their little group of developers that are *in* and everybody else can just go away. It's not like you can go submit a pull request to Newtonsoft JSON and hope to see it in the next set of release notes.</p></div>
	</div>

